body:
The maximum limit of 600,000 UNFI staked has been reached.  At 36% APR the staked UNFI is emitting 18,000 UNFI per month.  Since the whitepaper laid out a MAXIMUM monthly emission of 100,000 UNFI there is plenty of rewards to go around.  My proposal is to increase, on a regular basis, the amount available to be staked by AT LEAST the stake yield -18k this month, PLUS the migration rewards amount.  So for June the increase would be to a Maximum of 636,000. 600k+18k+15k+2k+1K

Increase by 36k UNFI:
18K from stake rewards;
15K Migration #5;
2K Migration #6;
1K Migration #7.

These newly distributed UNFI needs someplace to go or they might fine themselves selling on an exchange!
